title: Fear4Tez
description:
TEZOS COMMUNITY EVENTS is proud to present the 2nd Annual Friday the 13th Community Event - #FEAR4TEZ
We challenge you to give us a nightmare with your creepiest, scariest, and weirdest NFTs ever, filled with horrifying, superstitions, and bloody things (OR just be yourself, themes are fun but might not fit everyone). Full infos for artists to participate to this event are here.
